            <p class="text-justify">Viva Aerobus is a low-cost Mexican airline based in Monterrey International Airport, Mexico. It operates flights throughout Mexico and the United States with a fleet size of 57 aircraft. The airline also rewards its loyal customers who often fly with Viva Aerobus with a frequent flyer program called Viva Fun. </p>
